description: Lists Amazon QuickSight analyses that exist in the specified Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the analyses.

nested_items.name: AnalysisSummaryList
nested_items.description: Metadata describing each of the analyses that are listed.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the analysis.

nested_items.name: AnalysisId
nested_items.description: The ID of the analysis. This ID displays in the URL.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the analysis. This name is displayed in the Amazon QuickSight console.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The last known status for the analysis.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that the analysis was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that the analysis was last updated.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token that can be used in a subsequent request.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
